metadata.description:
This is the Genesis NFT for the infamous party series from the MGH DAO and Web3Go.  
This audioreactive artwork was created in collaboration with the Hungarian music producer [Máté Si](https://soundcloud.com/mate-sipos).  
The NFT will grant the owner access to all the MetaParties that will be hosted in the future.  
MetaPartyHub, redifining Web3 parties!
metadata.name: MetaPartyHub Devcon'22 feat Máté Si
